Heilbrunn Timeline of Art History: French Decorative Arts during the Reign of Louis XIV (1654–1715)
Description: This print is bound in Volume IV of Oeuvres.  Jombert published his collection of Le Pautre in 1751. Volume IV contains "desseins d'ornemens et trophées d'armes;"  This print is part of a series of six plates depicting friezes.  The series was originally published by Jean I Leblond.
